{"title":"windows安装python虚拟环境","date":"2019-08-05T16:00:00.000Z","link":"post/windows安装python虚拟环境","tags":["python"],"updated":"2019-08-06T01:42:18.000Z","content":"<p>使用virtualenv安装虚拟环境</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>使用虚拟环境安装Flask，可以避免包的混乱和版本的冲突，虚拟环境是Python解释器的副本，在虚拟环境中你可以安装扩展包，为每个程序单独创建的虚拟环境，可以保证程序只能访问虚拟环境中的包。而不会影响系统中安装的全局Python解释器，从而保证全局解释器的整洁。</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装\">安装<a href=\"post/windows安装python虚拟环境#安装\"></a></h2><p>安装virtualenv</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pip3 install virtualenv</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>安装virtualenv的win驱动</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pip3 install virtualenvwrapper-win</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"创建虚拟环境\">创建虚拟环境<a href=\"post/windows安装python虚拟环境#创建虚拟环境\"></a></h2><p>首先创建一个虚拟环境的目录，以flask_py为例。<br>进入目录中执行命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkvirtualenv Flask_py <span class=\"comment\">#将该目录设置成虚拟环境</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>执行后，自动启用了该虚拟环境。到这里安装便结束了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"命令\">命令<a href=\"post/windows安装python虚拟环境#命令\"></a></h2><p>进入虚拟环境<code>workon Flask.py</code><br>退出虚拟环境<code>deactivate Flask.py</code></p>\n","next":{"title":"Windows下安装部署Redis服务","link":"post/Windows下安装部署Redis服务"},"plink":"http://localhost:4000/post/windows安装python虚拟环境/","toc":[{"title":"安装","id":"安装","index":"1"},{"title":"创建虚拟环境","id":"创建虚拟环境","index":"2"},{"title":"命令","id":"命令","index":"3"}],"copyright":{"license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名(<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","author":"青崖","link":"<a href=\"http://localhost:4000/post/windows安装python虚拟环境/\" title=\"windows安装python虚拟环境\">http://localhost:4000/post/windows安装python虚拟环境/</a>"}}